Events.Text: Say hello to the AI assistant and ask for help (see instructions on the left). [instruction 1 of 6]
Hi, I need to make an appointment with Dr. Johnson today. Can you help me?
Try to get an appointment as soon as possible (right now it is 12 pm on Sunday). [instruction 2 of 6]
day
What day of the week would you like to schedule the appointment for?
Today as soon as possible if you can. Sunday.
Keep asking for other times until the assistant has found a slot for you. Engage in smalltalk once this is done. [instruction 3 of 6]
your name
Could I have your name, please?
Alexis
Say something about Dr. Johnson, the AI Assistant, or something that has happened to you today. Be creative! [instruction 4 of 6]
time
time
I can be there at 2 pm at the earliest. Check that time. Please hurry, I'm tired of feeling bad.
It occurs to you that you also want to make an appointment to get your kid John vaccinated. Perhaps you can schedule a second appointment at the same time? [instruction 5 of 6]
symptoms
Could you describe your symptoms, please?
Headache, dizziness, and muscle weakness for the last 2 days.
